        "name": "Devastating Duelist",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "You pointedly note your enemy's deficiencies, filling them with fear and dismay. Strike an opponent with your Aldori dueling sword.   \n  \nIf the Strike is successful, attempt a Dueling Lore check against the target's Will DC. On a success, the target becomes frightened 2. This is an emotion, fear, and mental effect.",
